vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; font-size: 12px; line-height: 0; top: -0.5em;\">2</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">。目前其南侧上海交通大学信息安全工程学院正在进行基坑施工，大部分区域底板已浇筑完成。</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">2019</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">4</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">月底，园区南侧地坪出现地坪开裂、地坪原有分仓缝明显变宽等损伤。由于近施工侧园区地坪内埋设较多管线，且园区房屋内有国家重点实验室。为策安全，</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">拟</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">对园区内房屋及其附属物（管道、室外地坪）进行现状完损状况检测、施工过程中沉降及裂缝监测、施工后完损复测。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 21px; line-height: 31.5px; font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 21px; line-height: 31.5px; font-family: 宋体;\">检测、监测依据</span></strong></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 48px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">[1]&nbsp;</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">委托方提供资料</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 48px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">[2]&nbsp;</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">现场踏勘情况</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 48px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">[3]&nbsp;</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">国家标准《建筑变形测量规程》</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">JGJ8-2016</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 48px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">[4]&nbsp;</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">国家标准《建筑结构检测技术标准》</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">GB/T0344-2004</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 48px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">[5]&nbsp;</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">国家标准《砌体结构设计规范》</span