>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">查阅建筑物原始图纸资料、基本结构体系及建筑物使用情况，</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">了解相邻基坑施工工程的工程概况、施工方案、施工进度计划及其对园区内房屋的有效保护措施，对园区地坪的监测数据等。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(2)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">调查建筑物室内外、周边地坪和围墙的裂缝与损坏现状，采用文字、图纸、照片等方法，记录房屋损坏部位、范围和程度等情况。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(3)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">对典型裂缝的部位设置石膏饼等监测标志，并记录裂缝位置、宽度等初始状态，为施工过程中房屋的监测提供条件。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(4)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">测量房屋的角点垂直度，利用房屋的外墙特征点测量房屋的相对不均匀沉降情况，为施工后的复测提供条件。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(5)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">在房屋的特征部位均匀地布设沉降测点，主要布设在墙角位置，采用水准测量闭合回路法，利用水准仪对设置在房屋上沉降测点的高程确定房屋各沉降测点的初始高程，为施工过程中的监测提供条件。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(6)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">园区地下管线探测及雨污水管损伤调查。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(7)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 