l-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">在相邻工程地下结构施工完毕后，对园区房屋及其附属物进行施工后检测，对受检房屋、室外地坪及地下雨污水管道进行完损复核，记录其的损坏部位和程度，通过与现状检测结果对比，可以客观的反映相邻基坑工程施工对园区内房屋及其附属物的影响程度。主要检测内容：</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(1)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">复查现状被检测房屋、室外地坪及地下雨污水管既有损伤发展状况，记录并测量其新增损伤的部位、范围及程度，具体检测内容和方法参照现状完损检测。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(2)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">对施工过程中沉降及裂缝监测的结果进行总结，分析房屋及室外地坪沉降及裂缝发展变化规律，绘制主要裂缝分布对比图和沉降曲线图。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(3)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span