: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">[11]&nbsp;</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">上海市工程建设规范《地基基础设计规范》</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">DGJ08-11-2010</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 48px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">[12]&nbsp;</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">上海市标准《地下管线测绘规范》</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">DGJ08-85-2000</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 21px; line-height: 31.5px; font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 21px; line-height: 31.5px; font-family: 宋体;\">检测工作内容</span></strong></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 56px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 21px; line-height: 31.5px; font-family: Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 19px; line-height: 28.5px; font-family: 楷体;\">现状检测</span></strong></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(1)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">查阅建筑物原始图纸资料、基本结构体系及建筑物使用情况，</span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">了解相邻基坑施工工程的工程概况、施工方案、施工进度计划及其对园区内房屋的有效保护措施，对园区地坪的监测数据等。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(2)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">调查建筑物室内外、周边地坪和围墙的裂缝与损坏现状，采用文字、图纸、照片等方法，记录房屋损坏部位、范围和程度等情况。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(3)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">对典型裂缝的部位设置石膏饼等监测标志，并记录裂缝位置、宽度等初始状态，为施工过程中房屋的监测提供条件。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(4)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">测量房屋的角点垂直度，利用房屋的外墙特征点测量房屋的相对不均匀沉降情况，为施工后的复测提供条件。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(5)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">在房屋的特征部位均匀地布设沉降测点，主要布设在墙角位置，采用水准测量闭合回路法，利用水准仪对设置在房屋上沉降测点的高程确定房屋各沉降测点的初始高程，为施工过程中的监测提供条件。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(6)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">园区地下管线探测及雨污水管损伤调查。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(7)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">分析房屋存在的薄弱环节，提出沉降变形与裂缝报警值，提供包括裂缝和沉降报警值的现状检测报告。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 56px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Wingdings; color: black;\">l<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 19px; line-height: 28.5px; font-family: 楷体;\">施工过程中监测</span></strong></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">通过相邻基坑工程施工过程中对园区内房屋及室外地坪进行沉降和裂缝变化情况监测，可以客观的了解工程施工过程中园区内房屋及室外地坪变形和损伤发展变化趋势。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 56px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 19px; line-height: 28.5px; font-family: 楷体;\">相邻地下工程施工后复测</span></strong></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">在相邻工程地下结构施工完毕后，对园区房屋及其附属物进行施工后检测，对受检房屋、室外地坪及地下雨污水管道进行完损复核，记录其的损坏部位和程度，通过与现状检测结果对比，可以客观的反映相邻基坑工程施工对园区内房屋及其附属物的影响程度。主要检测内容：</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(1)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">复查现状被检测房屋、室外地坪及地下雨污水管既有损伤发展状况，记录并测量其新增损伤的部位、范围及程度，具体检测内容和方法参照现状完损检测。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(2)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">对施工过程中沉降及裂缝监测的结果进行总结，分析房屋及室外地坪沉降及裂缝发展变化规律，绘制主要裂缝分布对比图和沉降曲线图。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(3)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">在现状检测报告和施工过程中监测数据的基础上，通过前后对比客观评定施工对房屋及附属物造成的影响。主要包括检测房屋、室外地坪及地下埋设管线基本情况、相邻工程概况、房屋受施工影响的损伤发展状况、监测工作总结及其受施工影响分析。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \">(4)<span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: \">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">根据被检测房屋及其附属物的损坏情况，给出检测结论及修缮建议。对于损伤可能继续发展或存在后续影响源的房屋及其附属物，提出继续加强监测的要求。</span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">对三阶段检测和监测工作进行总结，说明被检测房屋及其附属物受相邻工程施工影响的范围和程度，对目前房屋及其附属物的完损状况进行评价。</span><